io.debezium.document

Interface Array

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Array>, java.lang.Iterable<Array.Entry>

    public interface Array
extends java.lang.Iterable<Array.Entry>, java.lang.Comparable<Array>
    An array of Values. The array can also be viewed as a stream of Array.Entry instances, each of which contain the index and the value.
